                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-427" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES HALE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 100.) I was on duty, and saw the prosecutor with the prisoner in custody, and the handkerchief which he said he saw in the prisoner's hand—I never said it was not worth while to take him.</p>
